e\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533726\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xha1665702867265.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xha1665702867265.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xha1665702867265.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xha1665702867265\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Depending on the specific error, here are some possible causes.</p>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"xha1665702867265__section_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d739228e49\">\n Symptom: Enter Network Password dialog pops up when opening a Web page. The dialog also indicates: Realm <var class=\"keyword varname\">RealmName</var>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">AUTHORIZATION</code> is set to <var class=\"keyword varname\">RealmName</var> in\n                        the servlet properties of the URD servlet.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb__entry__2\">Remove the <code class=\"ph codeph\">AUTHORIZATION</code> servlet property of the URD\n                        servlet.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb__entry__1\">Incorrect Authentication Method set in the web server.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"xha1665702867265__table_kwl_q2p_hwb__entry__2\">Start Internet Service Manager and open Properties window of the item\n                        Default Web Site. Select the tab Directory Security. Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit\n                           for Anonymous Access and Authentication Control</span>. Only the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Allow Anonymous Access</span> check box should be\n                        selected.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"xha1665702867265__section_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d739228e115\">\n Symptom: Image on Server Page is not displayed in picture control.\n </h2>\n<div class=\"p\">With view source of HTML page, a line appears such\n            as:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xha1665702867265_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xha1665702867265__codeblock_ar4_t2p_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;IMG SRC=\"_GET_RESOURCE _?RESOURCENAME= error!!!\"&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xha1665702867265__table_iy4_s2p_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"xha1665702867265__table_iy4_s2p_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"xha1665702867265__table_iy4_s2p_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"xha1665702867265__table_iy4_s2p_hwb__entry__1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">RESOURCEDIR</code> setting of the URD Servlet Alias is not\n                        set to the correct location, for example <span class=\"ph filepath\">c:/webapps/wasvwww\n                           /resources</span> is set while <span class=\"ph filepath\">c:/webapps/wasvwww\n                           /resource</span> exists.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"xha1665702867265__table_iy4_s2p_hwb__entry__2\">Specify correct match between <code class=\"ph codeph\">RESOURCEDIR</code> and the\n                        resources directory.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533726\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533726\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "WRD Configuration Errors—Other Problems When Using Browser Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Depending on the specific error, here are some possible causes. Symptom: Enter Network Password dialog pops up when opening a Web page. The dialog also indicates: Realm RealmName Possible cause Resolution AUTHORIZATION is set to RealmName in the servlet properties of the URD servlet. Remove the AUTHORIZATION servlet property of the URD servlet. Incorrect Authentication Method set in the web server. Start Internet Service Manager and open Properties window of the item Default Web Site. Select the tab Directory Security. Click Edit for Anonymous Access and Authentication Control . Only the Allow Anonymous Access check box should be selected. Symptom: Image on Server Page is not displayed in picture control. With view source of HTML page, a line appears such as: Explain this code <IMG SRC=\"_GET_RESOURCE _?RESOURCENAME= error!!!\"> Copy Possible cause Resolution The RESOURCEDIR setting of the URD Servlet Alias is not set to the correct location, for example c:/webapps/wasvwww /resources is set while c:/webapps/wasvwww /resource exists. Specify correct match between RESOURCEDIR and the resources directory. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}